data.description: 5 acre country property w/charming cabin, barn & storage shed in the highly-desired Pecan Bend. 2 bed/2 bath cabin has been updated to an open floor plan & is equipped with a new HVAC system, new flooring, updated kitchen/bathrooms. Ideal property in the country to get away from the hustle & bustle. Pecan Bend backs to Brazos Bend State park, making wildlife plentiful including lots of deer. Residents also enjoy 2 private parks including River Park; a beach-like park along the banks of Brazos River where residents often ride 4-wheelers & have bon-fires. Plus Lake Park which boasts fishing & hiking around the 200-acre lake stocked full of fish. Additional community amenities include multiple boat ramps, a volunteer fire department, playground & recreation center. This is your chance to live in a peaceful oasis away from the big city, yet only 40 minutes to Sugar Land, 50 minutes to Downtown Houston & 50+ minutes to some Gulf Coast beaches.
